Description: A set of small corpora intended for use in corpus linguistic analysis. This is a data package that also provides a minimal set of utility functions to assist with reading the data into R. The corpora where prepared by the Centre for Corpus Research at the University of Birmingham (http://www.birmingham.ac.uk/research/activity/corpus/).
